http://www.nextgov.com/cybersecurity/2015/03/house-advances-cybersecurity-bill-despite-surveillance-fears/108544/?oref=ng-channeltopstory<br />
http://www.nextgov.com/cybersecurity/2015/03/house-advances-bill-combat-cybertheft/108493/?oref=ng-channelriver</p>
